{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561260/extras/STORE_Bed_new.png?t=1730354907\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561260/extras/NewGif_4.gif?t=1730354907\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Embark on a point &amp; click adventure set in an infinite hotel on the edge of collapse!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The ever-growing accommodation behemoth known as Hyperdrive Inn is your father\u2019s creation, and he is also responsible for triggering a set of cataclysmic events that threaten to destroy everything in existence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561260/extras/NewGif_3.gif?t=1730354907\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">He also happens to be the only person in the universe who can fix everything. Too bad he has gone missing. What\u2019s even worse: he went hiding somewhere in the infinite hotel of his. And to top it all off, you\u2019re the one who must hunt him down and save the day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561260/extras/NewGif_2.gif?t=1730354907\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561260/extras/STORE_Expect_new.png?t=1730354907\" />The infinite hotel of Hyperdrive Inn is filled with weird visitors (and inhabitants), outlandish environments and brain-twisting puzzles. You\u2019ll never know what you find, who you meet and where you end up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561260/extras/NewGif_5.gif?t=1730354907\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hyperdrive Inn is full of surprises, and who says you can\u2019t have fun while the world is coming to an end? After all, there are only two things that are infinite: the hotel and human stupidity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561260/extras/Steam1.png?t=1730354907\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Featuring plenty of oddball humor in the vein of those good old LucasArts titles, the world of Hyperdrive Inn is filled with references to popular culture and classic adventure games. It\u2019s like living your childhood again but trapped inside an ever-shifting monster that some people call a hotel. Who wouldn\u2019t like that!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561260/extras/STORE_Key_new.png?t=1730354907\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Classic 2D point &amp; click adventure with a modern touch</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Graphics made entirely from scanned fabric samples</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fully original score with Finnish folk music influences</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Replay value through randomized content</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Reached the Hyperdrive","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2561260/2a9442f5f23d2380595b5619192de3308584cfd8.jpg"},{"name":"Disabled the Hyperdive","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2561260/d2e2bfc9aa78129e188407e22b93f2566fea2676.jpg"},{"name":"Happy Birthday!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2561260/04c2e014cce72b36d966beeec7be783843c0bca1.jpg"},{"name":"Gaming with dad","path":"h